1
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:13,520
Song Huainan, oh, Song Huainan.

2
00:00:14,160 --> 00:00:18,240
Seeing your Song family cursed as traitors,

3
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:20,280
really gives me great pleasure.

4
00:00:20,480 --> 00:00:23,520
Finally, someone has exposed

5
00:00:23,520 --> 00:00:25,160
your dirty deeds.

6
00:00:28,160 --> 00:00:29,820
The Song family is in trouble,

7
00:00:29,840 --> 00:00:32,369
yet you still have time to scold Song Huainan.

8
00:00:32,640 --> 00:00:34,970
Shengsheng married into the Song family.

9
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:36,640
If something happens to the Song family,

10
00:00:36,640 --> 00:00:38,440
Shengsheng won't have an easy time.

11
00:00:38,440 --> 00:00:41,040
Shengsheng is a daughter of the Yao family.

12
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:43,720
What does the Song family have to do with her?

13
00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:49,410
Where are you going?

14
00:00:52,680 --> 00:00:54,340
I'm going to find Shengsheng.

15
00:00:54,760 --> 00:00:55,760
You are not going.

16
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:00,120
Why?

17
00:01:00,440 --> 00:01:02,240
Aren't you worried about her at all?

18
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:06,200
You should focus on the soap factory,

19
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:07,520
not go out every day

20
00:01:07,520 --> 00:01:09,760
painting your face like an actor.

21
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:13,080
I'm going to see Shengsheng.

22
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:14,840
Yao Lifu,

23
00:01:15,320 --> 00:01:17,200
put away your little schemes.

24
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:19,120
If you're counting on Song Huainan

25
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:21,120
to be the Yao family's backer,

26
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:22,200
forget it.

27
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:23,720
If something happens to you...

28
00:01:23,720 --> 00:01:25,800
He doesn't care if you live or die.

29
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:28,490
Once the soap factory is up and running

30
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:30,720
and we get Johnson's order,

31
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:33,080
by then, Song Huainan

32
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:35,539
will be out of the picture.

33
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:40,039
If Song Huainan finds out you have an agenda,

34
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:41,640
will he spare Shengsheng?

35
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:44,800
Even if you're guarding against Song Huainan,

36
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:45,960
can you guarantee

37
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:48,090
he isn't suspicious of the Yao family?

38
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:52,900
And another thing.

39
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:55,200
I am not a mere actor.

40
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:57,759
It is my dedication

41
00:01:57,759 --> 00:02:00,080
and passion for this art.

42
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:05,960
Forget it.

43
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:08,560
You wouldn't understand even if I told you.

44
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:20,520
Huainan.

45
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:23,440
I've come up with a good solution.

46
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:24,800
Just tell everyone

47
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:26,240
that your cooperation with the foreigners

48
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:28,400
is to bring more benefits to the people

49
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:30,360
and provide more job opportunities.

50
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:32,440
That way, the Song family's reputation

51
00:02:32,440 --> 00:02:34,370
can be turned around immediately.

52
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:36,440
Reporting.

53
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:38,280
Come in.

54
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:03,320
So you thought of it long ago.

55
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:06,720
Mr. Yao, if there's nothing else,

56
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,240
please leave.

57
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:10,400
Huainan.

58
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:16,520
How are things with you and Shengsheng?

59
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:19,840
Shengsheng was spoiled growing up.

60
00:03:20,079 --> 00:03:21,800
If she ever upsets you...

61
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,400
Shengsheng and I are newlyweds.

62
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:27,440
Why would she upset me?

63
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:29,900
I have other matters to attend to.

64
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:33,840
Mr. Yao, please.

65
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:58,060
Young Marshal.

66
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,490
Let's talk this out.

67
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:01,820
What's the result?

68
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,560
What? What result?

69
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,890
Don't play dumb with me.

70
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:06,640
Tell me the result.

71
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:08,200
Is it poisonous or not?

72
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,040
Yes.

73
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:11,960
No.

74
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:14,440
Doctor, think carefully before you answer me.

75
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:15,160
No poison.

76
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:18,860
Since there's no poison, give me the report.

77
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,000
As for the Commander,

78
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,400
you know what to say.

79
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:25,200
Yes.

80
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:26,760
Yes.

81
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:37,000
Commander, the test results are in.

82
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:38,640
What are the results?

83
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:39,440
No poison.

84
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:49,620
I hope I was just overthinking it.

85
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,840
Song Qingzhou, what are you doing?

86
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:16,370
I have something to ask you.

87
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:18,880
You stole the contract and bribed the newspaper

88
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:21,080
to declare the Song family as traitors.

89
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:24,170
Did you do it to destroy our family?

90
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:27,880
Song Qingzhou, over such a small matter,

91
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:29,080
you're turning against me?

92
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:30,720
A small matter?

93
00:05:32,320 --> 00:05:33,320
In that case,

94
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,720
there must be something bigger.

95
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:41,640
Tell me about it,

96
00:05:42,320 --> 00:05:43,920
so I can prepare myself.

97
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,330
Have you ever wondered,

98
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:50,810
since your mother is alive,

99
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:53,320
why she hasn't returned to the Song family to find you?

100
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:54,980
You have news about my mother?

101
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:58,200
Information was scarce before,

102
00:05:58,200 --> 00:06:00,200
but I've found some leads recently.

103
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,200
I believe

104
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:03,960
I'll find out where she is very soon.

105
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,600
It better be.

106
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,650
I'll wait for your results.

107
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:17,280
Yao Shengsheng, I can tolerate your habitual lying,

108
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:19,320
but when it comes to my mother,

109
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,180
you'd better not lie to me.

110
00:06:26,080 --> 00:06:26,920
Otherwise,

111
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,760
I'll make you wish you were dead.

112
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:42,490
Now with double the poison,

113
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:45,880
it'll feel like a thousand arrows piercing your stomach.

114
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:49,680
This poison will rot your guts.

115
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:53,659
You'll suffer for seven days and nights before you die.

116
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:56,280
It suits you perfectly.

117
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:58,840
Song Qingzhou, you bastard.

118
00:06:58,960 --> 00:07:02,200
Enjoy the taste of hell.

119
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,200
You unfilial son!

120
00:07:28,960 --> 00:07:29,800
Get in here!

121
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:36,120
Did you go see Song Huainan?

122
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:42,000
For Song Huainan, such a small matter

123
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,520
can be solved in no time.

124
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:46,740
Don't think I don't know your little scheme.

125
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:51,200
Rest assured.

126
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:54,040
Between Song Huainan and me,

127
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:55,620
there is nothing left.

128
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:01,610
Father, let's not talk about this.

129
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:04,090
Shengsheng's birthday is next month.

130
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:06,920
Why don't we bring her back to celebrate?

131
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:10,920
Our family hasn't been together for a long time.

132
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:14,640
Shengsheng belongs to the Song family now.

133
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:15,800
As for her birthday,

134
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:18,120
the Song family will surely handle it.

135
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:19,380
How about this?

136
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:22,640
Go to the storeroom and pick some decent gifts,

137
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:23,770
then send them over.

138
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,920
Okay, I'll go prepare.

139
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:38,320
You schemed to get close to the Song family.

140
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:40,159
What exactly do you want?

141
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:56,480
Can I still trust you?

142
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:58,880
I feel

143
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:01,680
much better than before.

144
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:05,240
You gave me the antidote,

145
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,040
not poison.

146
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:19,120
You only feel better

147
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:22,330
because of your dying hallucination.

148
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:26,000
You can't bear to lose me,

149
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:28,560
so how could you let me die?
